attributes.Long form description: The student is repairing a chair. They grab the seat and unscrew it, and then align the legs. They check the screws and washers, and then tighten the middle bolt on the legs. They screw the legs back on, and then flip and check the chair.

attributes.Transcription: Hello and thank you for taking part in our study. In front of you, you will see the Marius stool by IKEA.
Your task for now would be to please assemble it.
You may now begin, thank you.

attributes.Action sentence: The student aligns the legs of the chair.

attributes.Transcription: First, please take the two feet and place now vertically on the table. In a upright position.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should flip the leg.

attributes.Transcription: Please, flip it.
Thank you.
Please put the base board on the table. And please take the nuts and bolt.
Please take the bolt.
Please put the wrench back on the table, on the left-hand side, you ll see a long metal bolt.
So to the left of the board, there would be once one screw.  Please also take the nuts, that is the small circular metal piece.
Thank you.
Please use the ranch provided to tight the nut.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the  hexagonal wrench.

attributes.Transcription: Please make sure not to over tighten the nut.
Thank you.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should make sure not to over tight the nut.

attributes.Transcription: Please make sure not to over tight the nut.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the leg and the seat.

attributes.Transcription: Please put the base back at the table and please take the feet and place them on the top of the base board.

attributes.Transcription: More over please, make sure your hands in the camera view thank you.

attributes.Action sentence: The student flips and checks the bolt of the chair.

attributes.Transcription: Please flip this stool and tighten the center screw.
